<br>
Bonebite<br>
   <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19854">everquest.allakhazam.com/...item=19854</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <br>
