<br>
The rings is sooooooo much better a reward for the amount of time spent camping, heh.<br>
<br>
But hey, if you can snag the items, the DPS is decent, the aggro is ok becaus it's such a fast acting DoT so it makes a nice offhander to team with, say, Frostbringer.<br>
